Tomas Berdych and his model girlfriend Ester Satorova have announced the news of their engagement ahead of upcoming Australian Open match against Jurgen Melzer.

The men's seventh seed, Berdych and the Czech model  began dating in the autumn of 2012 after his long-time relationship with WTA player Lucie Safarova ended. 

Clearly excited about the news, TV presenter and model Rachael Finch, who interviewed the duo for Australia's Channel Seven, shared the news on her Instagram page along with a shot of a gondola.

